      Form
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Enrol with the Rural Payments Agency to export hops to the EU
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">To export hops and hops products to the European Union (EU), you must enrol with the Rural Payments Agency (RPA) before you can apply for and receive Attestations of Equivalence (AoE).</p>

  </div>
</div>

